===Noun===
'''drugget''' (''pl.'' '''druggets''')
#{{uncountable}} An inexpensive [[coarse]] [[wool]]en [[cloth]], used as a covering for finer [[carpet]]s, as a layer between the carpet and the [[floor]], or as a cheap floor covering on its own.
#{{countable}} A floor covering made of drugget.
